{"tid":2377480,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果白警同黑警打","createTime":"2021-01-23T15:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T00:17:15.000Z","uid":384355,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"579edacb05c1dfae029d167a5ee1a0db6a2509d0","tid":2377480,"uid":384355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T15:58:12.000Z","msg":"頭先係藍屍親戚屋企睇狗方「攻城」<br />\n<br />\n我睇完之後有咩感想<br />\n<br />\n1:恐怖分子咩會衝出嚟畀你射呀，我打war game都射唔中人啦，日日匿埋障礙物後面啦<br />\n<br />\n2:恐怖分子有防彈衣，同埋佢哋有受訓練，冇訓練佢都唔識開槍啦，仲有佢地知道如何保護自己，點會咁快死<br />\n<br />\n3:鄧pk 有參與其中，片段中有參與激戰，之後幫狗執手尾，扮好心做大事，實際上佢日日坐喺辦公室<br />\n<br />\n4:恐怖分子蠢L到，五個娃娃兵仲勁過佢地<br />\n<br />\n5:有真實感但同現實完全唔符合<br />\n<br />\n6:如果黑警同白警打，我唔知有幾精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1965b50da94cfd62c358d01a2460abc69ad8cd","tid":2377480,"uid":384355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:01:12.000Z","msg":"黑警同白警嘅實力差唔多，如果兩個交戰，兩方死仲多"},{"pid":"7a1f24e0cf8538345c95a231a3d6f002870cf997","tid":2377480,"uid":137704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:01:32.000Z","msg":"睇下啟晴邨單野就知真係有恐怖分子就唔會咁喇"},{"pid":"e0e3dfdb99492d9c1d57398f0ba71cb5d551809a","tid":2377480,"uid":280261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:02:24.000Z","msg":"無睇過。黑警"},{"pid":"02a10cfd973816aad44ca7fadf156907852345f8","tid":2377480,"uid":60733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:03:33.000Z","msg":"無睇過，黑警"},{"pid":"d01a7c89173c0b151745a28bf88e16a5e59e012f","tid":2377480,"uid":384355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e0e3dfdb99492d9c1d57398f0ba71cb5d551809a","tid":2377480,"uid":280261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:02:24.000Z","msg":"無睇過。黑警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:03:44.000Z","msg":"其實冇內容，動作片嚟"},{"pid":"f5edcde285ef4b07472c5bf2b80b261e45018dd0","tid":2377480,"uid":293261,"like":3,"dis